        "image": "shopify://shop_images/watch_e6529ab4-5ab4-48e4-a548-8596a05e7e92.jpg",
        "image_width": 500,
        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "watch & clock repairs",
        "text": "<p>We specialise in quality watch and clock repairs, servicing all brands at competitive prices. Batteries for all quartz watches are available while you wait. We take pride in the skill of our highly trained watchmakers, who regularly work on both contemporary and vintage timepieces. Despite advances in technology, modern watches still require upkeep, battery and capacitor replacement, rubber gaskets, watch band replacement, glasses, winders, the list goes on. Be assured that the utmost care will be taken with your precious timepiece. Visit us today for a new battery, free repair estimate or, better yet, a brilliant new timepiece for your collection.</p>",
