        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "we buy gold",
        "text": "<p>If you have scrap pieces of gold, unwanted or damaged jewellery, why not convert it to cash? Our professional staff are fully equipped to test your scrap and quote to convert to cash. Perhaps that damaged jewellery has sentimental value? Well let’s melt your gold down and work together to design a new heirloom from yesterday’s treasures.</p>",
